snippet.title: Amber Heard Names Dog After Australian Deputy Prime Minister In Pet Quarantine Spat
snippet.description:
✅ Listen Music in video here:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m7UvxaDGc_Q&list=PL3TfGl2m4jwAyLYBRY2uKBCzsvCiOwo8g&t=0s
Actor Amber Heard has named her new dog after Australian Deputy Prime Minister Barnaby Joyce years after her row over a required rabies pet quarantine while she was staying in the country. 
“Meet the newest member of the Heard family, Barnaby Joyce!” Heard tweeted on Sunday holding her new dog.
